  "Return the next line in the buffer, leaving point following it.\n
Return nil at `end-of-buffer'.\n
:EXAMPLE\n\n(mon-line-get-next)\nBubba on a line.\n
\(save-excursion \(equal \(mon-line-get-next\) \"\"\)\)\n
